root: ^SCIENTIST: It's good to see that someone else cares about legacy as well.
^ME: So, how do we send out this message? Do we have everything?
^SCIENTIST: I've collected enough evidence so that nobody can deny Drump did this to us. It's just a matter of sending it to the remaining governments of Earth.
^SCIENTIST: That's where you come in. You have to go to the computer over there and send it.
